  "texts": [
    "With the world being more aware of the situation, and the international community supporting Ukraine in various ways 65, 66, users likely have less reasons to continue tweeting in English.",
    "Instead, they return back to intra-national discussions and thus their native language(s).",
    "Limitations.",
    "We recognize that while our study provides a strong foundation towards a better understanding on how the Ukrainian population reacted to the Russian invasion both on-and offline, possible limitations need to be acknowledged.",
    "The sample of users investigated here is not representative of the entire Ukrainian population."
  ]
}